v 3
d statashiny. Build interactive HTML dashboards, calculators, and data tables from Stata
d
d statashiny generates standalone, interactive HTML dashboards from Stata
d using Bootstrap 5 (layout), DataTables (searchable/sortable tables), and
d Chart.js (live charts). Define numeric and checkbox inputs, value cards,
d data tables from variables in memory, and JavaScript-driven visualizations
d that recompute in the browser -- no web-dev required. Output is a single
d self-contained .html file you can email, host, or embed via <iframe>
d (pairs naturally with webdoc2 reports).
d
d KW: dashboard
d KW: html
d KW: interactive
d KW: bootstrap
d KW: datatables
d KW: chartjs
d KW: reporting
d KW: visualization
d
d Requires: Stata version 16
